<MainLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} mainClass="bg-background-200">
  <article class="prose prose-gray max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1>Terms and Conditions</h1>
    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 01-Jan-2025</p>

    <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
    <p>
      By accessing or using UsagePricing.com, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree, do not use the service.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Services Offered</h2>
    <p>
      UsagePricing.com provides a freemium SaaS platform to create and embed usage-based pricing calculators.
    </p>

    <h2>3. Account Responsibilities</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>You must be 18 years or older to create an account</li>
      <li>You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account credentials</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>4. Payment and Subscription</h2>
    <p>
      Paid plans are billed monthly/annually via Stripe. Subscriptions auto-renew unless cancelled.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Acceptable Use</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>No illegal or harmful usage</li>
      <li>No abuse, spam, or resource exhaustion</li>
      <li>No reverse engineering of the platform</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Termination</h2>
    <p>
      We reserve the right to suspend or terminate accounts that violate these Terms.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Disclaimer</h2>
    <p>
      The service is provided “as is” without warranties. We are not liable for any indirect damages or data loss.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Governing Law</h2>
    <p>
      These terms are governed by the laws of India. Disputes shall be resolved in the courts of Bengaluru, India.
    </p>
  </article>
</MainLayout>
